		<article class="post-8364 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-allposts category-financeeconomy tag-bank tag-bernanke tag-bonds tag-china tag-debt tag-dollar tag-economy tag-fiat tag-gold tag-gold-standard tag-monetary-policy tag-money tag-qe tag-reserve-currency tag-ron-paul tag-united-states post-listing">
			
