				<h1 class="name post-title entry-title" itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Thing"><span itemprop="name">Signs of the gold standard emerging in China?</span></h1>

				
				<div class="entry">
					<div class="share-post">
	<span class="share-text">Share !</span>
